      <title>贝莱德称 FDIC 计划将损害投资者利益并给银行带来成本</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/blackrock-says-fdic-proposal-would-hurt-investors-cost-banks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝莱德公司呼吁美国联邦存款保险公司迅速撤回对基金经理在银行持股比例的限制提议，称规则的改变将颠覆指数基金，提高银行筹集资金的成本，并扰乱经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/blackrock-says-fdic-proposal-would-hurt-investors-cost-banks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 24 Oct 2024 19:30:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
